title: NFL Week 10 Preview, Rams OT Andrew Whitworth, & Playoff Odds!
itunes:title: NFL Week 10 Preview, Rams OT Andrew Whitworth, & Playoff Odds!
description:
Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith use predictive analytics to predict which teams are most likely to end up in the NFL Playoffs this year, as well as winners and losers for all of this Week 10's NFL games. Cynthia also had a chance to sit down with Los Angeles Rams OT Andrew Whitworth to talk about why he was ready for a new challenge after 11 years with the Cincinnati Bengals.
